<item>
            <title>[LU-47] lbuild should use the ustar format to allow path names greater than 99</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-47</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is a continuation of bz 21581. Bernd had submitted a patch to move to using the pax format, but Brian pointed out that the ustar format is more compatible and would still increase the path length to 255 chars. We never followed up to change it though, so it still needs to be addressed. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
